text: Bothwell Chapungu (born 22 November 1987) is a Zimbabwean first-class cricketer. He was included in Zimbabwe's squad for the 2016 Africa T20 Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Zimbabwean cricketers Category:Centrals cricketers Category:Mid West Rhinos cricketers Category:Midlands cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Kwekwe
